WEBVTT

00:07.292 --> 00:08.958
[WIND WHISTLES]

00:26.875 --> 00:28.083
[METAL SQUEAKS]

00:31.667 --> 00:33.583
[THUNDER RUMBLES]
- [RAIN PATTERS]

00:43.667 --> 00:45.083
[WOOD CREAKS]

00:54.500 --> 00:55.958
[HEART BEATS SLOWLY]

01:00.917 --> 01:02.083
[WOMAN MOANS FAINTLY]

01:05.333 --> 01:06.667
[HEART BEATS FASTER]

01:17.375 --> 01:19.042
[ERIC, VO]:
I did everything for her.

01:20.917 --> 01:22.042
Gave her everything.

01:25.583 --> 01:27.458
How can everything not be enough?

01:37.000 --> 01:40.833
[CHOIR SINGS]
♪ Abide with me ♪

01:40.875 --> 01:46.875
♪ Fast falls the eventide ♪

01:47.625 --> 01:52.458
♪ The darkness deepens ♪

01:52.583 --> 01:57.792
♪ Lord, with me abide ♪

01:58.375 --> 02:04.333
♪ When other helpers fail ♪

02:04.375 --> 02:08.667
♪ And comforts flee ♪

02:09.208 --> 02:13.042
♪ Help of the hopeless ♪

02:13.083 --> 02:17.208
♪ Oh, abide with me ♪

02:17.250 --> 02:18.583
[SINGING DISTORTS AND FADES]

02:26.292 --> 02:28.375
[ERIC, VO]:
I sleep a lot.

02:30.458 --> 02:32.125
[HE STUTTERS]
The... the dreams.

02:34.667 --> 02:36.167
Oh God, the dreams.

02:42.625 --> 02:44.333
[PRIEST TALKS IN DISTANCE]

02:46.708 --> 02:48.542
[INDISTINCT VOICES OVERLAP]

02:57.667 --> 02:59.250
[HAUNTING VOICES ECHO]

03:00.292 --> 03:01.667
[BABY WAILS]

03:03.875 --> 03:05.542
[INDISTINCT VOICES WHISPER]

03:24.542 --> 03:26.292
[HAUNTING VOICES GROW LOUDER]

03:29.917 --> 03:31.375
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

03:40.458 --> 03:41.375
[COFFIN CRACKS]

03:50.500 --> 03:51.375
[HE SCREAMS SILENTLY]

03:51.458 --> 03:55.292
[ALARM CLOCK BLARES]

03:59.250 --> 04:00.333
[ALARM STOPS]

04:20.541 --> 04:21.875
[DOG WHIMPERS AND SCRATCHES]

04:22.792 --> 04:23.833
[DOG WHINES]

04:24.375 --> 04:25.458
Hey.

04:27.667 --> 04:28.667
Hey.

04:30.625 --> 04:31.583
I know.

04:32.250 --> 04:33.292
I know.

04:34.875 --> 04:35.875
I know.

04:36.000 --> 04:37.000
Yes.

04:38.333 --> 04:40.458
[SHIPPING NEWS ON RADIO]:
Variable three or less...

04:40.542 --> 04:43.375
[ERIC ON PHONE]: Yeah, I know.
Um... I'm... I'm sorry.

04:43.458 --> 04:45.167
I... I just can't make it in.

04:45.917 --> 04:47.833
[SHIPPING NEWS]:
...40s, easterly...

04:47.875 --> 04:49.042
[ERIC]:
Yeah, I understand.

04:49.708 --> 04:51.333
[SHIPPING NEWS]:
...occasionally six at first...

04:51.417 --> 04:52.333
No, I know it has.

04:52.417 --> 04:54.917
[SHIPPING NEWS]: ...becoming variable
three or less for a tide.

04:55.167 --> 04:56.208
Showers: good.

04:56.250 --> 04:58.625
[ERIC]:
I just still need the space... is all.

04:59.250 --> 05:01.792
[SHIPPING NEWS]:
East banking northeast, four or five.

05:02.250 --> 05:03.208
Thanks.

05:03.542 --> 05:04.583
[ERIC REPLACES RECEIVER]

05:04.625 --> 05:06.958
[SHIPPING NEWS]:
Rain, then showers: good, occasional.

05:08.125 --> 05:12.667
Southeast banking east-north-east:
five, occasionally six:

05:13.292 --> 05:14.708
rain or showers.

05:14.750 --> 05:16.083
[DOG EATS NOISILY]

05:16.625 --> 05:18.292
[DOG EATING MUFFLES RADIO]

05:25.708 --> 05:27.417
[DOG EATING NOISE GETS LOUDER]

05:29.417 --> 05:30.458
[EATING NOISE STOPS]

05:31.167 --> 05:33.667
[SHIPPING NEWS]: Good,
occasionally moderate in west country.

05:35.333 --> 05:36.542
[SHIPPING NEWS CONTINUES]

05:42.750 --> 05:46.500
Wight, Portland, Plymouth
variable two to four

05:46.542 --> 05:47.917
becoming northeasterly...

05:48.542 --> 05:50.375
[BABY MURMURS]

05:53.000 --> 05:55.000
[DRAWER CREAKS OPEN]
- [BABY MURMURS]

05:57.000 --> 05:58.083
[BABY WHIMPERS]

06:39.125 --> 06:40.042
[SHIPPING NEWS]:
Good.

06:41.042 --> 06:45.000
FitzRoy, Sole, north five or six,
occasionally poor...

06:51.542 --> 06:53.250
[PHONE RINGS]

07:12.708 --> 07:14.250
[PHONE STOPS RINGING]

07:17.167 --> 07:18.625
[SHIPPING NEWS]:
Northeast five or six.

07:18.708 --> 07:19.667
Decreasing four...

09:43.250 --> 09:44.583
[CAR ENGINE STOPS]

09:49.167 --> 09:50.292
Stay there, lad.

10:29.500 --> 10:30.917
[SHEEP BLEATS IN DISTANCE]

10:57.625 --> 10:58.667
Yes?

11:03.750 --> 11:04.792
Place is a mess.

11:14.083 --> 11:15.292
I'm coming back.

11:16.750 --> 11:18.667
No. No, you're not.

11:19.833 --> 11:21.083
I don't need you.

11:23.125 --> 11:24.458
What about what I need?

11:24.500 --> 11:25.667
What you need?

11:27.083 --> 11:28.333
What you need?

11:29.250 --> 11:30.667
What do you need, Eric?

11:30.708 --> 11:31.708
Mum...

11:31.750 --> 11:34.333
You left your father here alone.

11:34.417 --> 11:36.625
You left him here because of her.

11:38.292 --> 11:39.375
Rachel.

11:39.833 --> 11:41.292
You're still wearing her ring.

11:42.250 --> 11:44.208
[SHE SIGHS]
And after what she did.

11:45.083 --> 11:46.667
Ungodly woman.

11:48.375 --> 11:51.417
We're nothing without faith, Eric.

11:54.583 --> 11:56.167
Faith didn't save Dad, Mum.

11:58.875 --> 12:01.875
Just... look what it's done to you.

12:02.708 --> 12:05.500
No. No, you did this to me.

12:05.833 --> 12:07.917
You're only here now
because she's dead.

12:07.958 --> 12:11.333
You've no place talking about my wife!
- And you've no place here.

12:12.958 --> 12:14.167
You can go.

12:14.583 --> 12:17.083
I learnt to cope the hard way.

12:17.583 --> 12:19.125
It's time you did the same.

12:33.875 --> 12:34.917
Where will you go?

12:38.625 --> 12:39.667
Eric.

12:46.167 --> 12:47.167
Don't worry.

12:48.292 --> 12:49.458
[CAR ENGINE STARTS]

12:49.750 --> 12:50.833
Eric...

13:01.333 --> 13:03.083
[CROW CAWS]

13:22.833 --> 13:25.458
[THUNDER RUMBLES]
- [WIND WHISTLES]

14:37.750 --> 14:38.750
[HE INHALES SHARPLY]

14:41.125 --> 14:42.208
[HE CRIES]

14:51.000 --> 14:52.167
[HE SOBS]

15:05.292 --> 15:06.458
[SHEEP BLEATS]

15:57.125 --> 15:58.292
[ERIC FLICKS LIGHTER OPEN]

16:08.458 --> 16:09.667
[HE FLICKS LIGHTER SHUT]

16:22.208 --> 16:23.083
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Smoker?

16:28.833 --> 16:29.875
No.

16:35.125 --> 16:36.125
Was my wife's.

16:37.917 --> 16:39.333
She not joining you?

16:44.458 --> 16:46.000
Escaping or running?

16:54.542 --> 16:56.333
I just needed the work is all.

16:57.875 --> 17:00.042
And how did the advert find you?

17:02.375 --> 17:03.542
I saw it in the paper.

17:03.750 --> 17:07.458
No. How did it find you?

17:11.750 --> 17:14.208
Sometimes people just
need solitude, you know?

17:17.166 --> 17:19.208
Breathing space, Mr Black.

17:20.291 --> 17:22.000
Just that, right?
- [DOG WHIMPERS]

17:24.666 --> 17:25.750
Yeah.

17:50.792 --> 17:51.917
Bax, come on.

17:54.125 --> 17:55.208
Come on.

17:57.125 --> 17:58.208
Come on.

17:58.833 --> 17:59.833
Hey, come on.

18:07.042 --> 18:08.500
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

18:10.000 --> 18:11.625
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Bell's for the fog.

18:12.042 --> 18:13.458
Hits hard out here.

18:14.250 --> 18:16.250
The light stopped years back.

18:31.375 --> 18:32.833
The old cottage.

18:33.500 --> 18:34.750
That's your home now.

18:34.833 --> 18:36.667
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

18:41.625 --> 18:43.833
As you know, the generator's buggered.

18:43.917 --> 18:46.708
Round the back there if you fancy
trying to fix it yourself.

18:47.083 --> 18:48.958
Gas lamps by the dozen inside.

18:49.792 --> 18:51.500
Plenty of firewood and fuel.

18:52.208 --> 18:56.042
There's a telephone for emergencies,
though it gets cut off by bad weather.

18:57.292 --> 18:59.542
It's easy to get lost here, so be warned.

19:00.625 --> 19:02.917
You've got your instructions and your map.

19:06.042 --> 19:07.042
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

19:07.125 --> 19:08.208
So you'll be fine.

19:11.458 --> 19:12.875
So...

19:12.958 --> 19:14.583
You're just leaving now?

19:18.167 --> 19:19.542
It's not my place here.

19:21.917 --> 19:23.125
When will you be back?

19:23.208 --> 19:25.375
I'll be back next Tuesday with supplies.

19:25.750 --> 19:27.583
Anything else you need, you let me know.

19:29.167 --> 19:30.125
OK.

19:30.167 --> 19:32.000
[FISHERWOMAN]:
You've got some sheep to find.

19:32.167 --> 19:33.875
Best get to it, Mr Black.

19:34.250 --> 19:35.292
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

19:35.375 --> 19:37.750
You'll not be short of chores here,
that's for sure.

19:40.375 --> 19:41.542
I nearly forgot.

19:44.042 --> 19:45.250
You'll be needing this.

19:45.667 --> 19:48.833
A journal. Keep it safe.

19:51.708 --> 19:52.708
Good luck.

20:00.083 --> 20:02.458
Something's haunting you, Mr Black.

20:03.542 --> 20:04.958
I can see it.

20:11.417 --> 20:13.583
Hope you get the chance to confront it.

20:19.583 --> 20:21.167
[DOG WHIMPERS]

20:23.958 --> 20:25.333
Yeah, you said it, lad.

20:33.583 --> 20:34.958
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

20:51.917 --> 20:53.500
[DOOR OPENS]

21:04.042 --> 21:05.917
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]
- [HE WHISTLES TO DOG]

21:09.208 --> 21:10.375
[DOG WHIMPERS]

21:22.917 --> 21:23.917
[ERIC]:
Christ.

21:42.708 --> 21:43.958
[DOG WHINES]

21:44.833 --> 21:46.125
[DOG WHIMPERS]

22:04.333 --> 22:06.750
[NO DIAL TONE]

22:18.583 --> 22:20.208
[NO WATER RUNS]

22:20.875 --> 22:22.750
[HOUSE CREAKS]
- Shit.

23:13.083 --> 23:14.250
[SHEEP BLEAT]

23:21.292 --> 23:22.375
Come.

24:16.750 --> 24:18.417
[DOG WHIMPERS]
- Good boy.

24:22.500 --> 24:23.500
Come on.

24:35.792 --> 24:36.958
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

24:58.458 --> 25:00.208
[HOUSE CREAKS AND GROANS]

25:05.833 --> 25:07.292
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

25:14.917 --> 25:16.417
[HOUSE CREAKS]

25:25.875 --> 25:27.583
[CLOCK TICKS]

26:12.125 --> 26:13.417
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

26:22.208 --> 26:23.917
[SHEEP BLEAT]

26:48.417 --> 26:51.167
One, two, three, four...

26:51.333 --> 26:52.375
[SHEEP BLEAT]

26:52.417 --> 26:54.708
One, two... Shit.

27:00.625 --> 27:03.292
Just put them there. Got it.

27:08.667 --> 27:10.250
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

27:15.708 --> 27:16.792
[HE COUGHS]

27:35.542 --> 27:37.375
Hey, what are you lookin' at?

27:43.125 --> 27:44.125
[DOG WHIMPERS]

27:45.625 --> 27:47.292
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

27:48.042 --> 27:49.792
Oh, it's locked up, no?

27:57.792 --> 27:58.750
Come on.

28:00.250 --> 28:01.417
[HE WHISTLES TO DOG]

28:03.417 --> 28:05.708
Come on. Come on.
- [DOG WHIMPERS]

28:13.625 --> 28:15.000
[CLOCK TICKS]

28:22.917 --> 28:24.792
[WAVES LAP SHORE]

28:28.417 --> 28:29.750
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

28:29.792 --> 28:31.250
[CLOCK TICKS]

28:36.125 --> 28:37.625
[TICKING SLOWS DOWN]

28:44.833 --> 28:46.125
[TICKING STOPS]

29:08.042 --> 29:10.750
What a day. Eh, Bax?
- [DOG WHIMPERS]

29:13.417 --> 29:14.500
What a place.

29:15.750 --> 29:18.167
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

29:22.417 --> 29:23.833
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

29:40.542 --> 29:42.125
[HOUSE CREAKS]

