29:52.292 --> 29:53.875
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

29:54.375 --> 29:56.208
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

30:06.042 --> 30:08.208
[CLOCK TICKS]

30:08.375 --> 30:10.292
[HOUSE CREAKS]

30:15.125 --> 30:17.000
[INDISTINCT WHISPERING VOICES]

30:18.917 --> 30:20.292
