30:20.375 --> 30:21.750
[CLOCK STOPS TICKING]

30:25.875 --> 30:27.667
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

30:41.958 --> 30:43.583
[WIND WHISTLES]

30:49.833 --> 30:51.542
[DOG WHINES]

30:52.875 --> 30:54.375
[DOG WHIMPERS]

30:55.625 --> 30:57.333
Should've got a job with a bungalow.

30:58.167 --> 30:59.250
[HE DROPS BAG ON FLOOR]

31:00.417 --> 31:01.667
Don't look at me like that.

31:02.167 --> 31:04.833
I'm not staying down here.
- [DOG WHINES]

31:09.250 --> 31:11.000
OK, I need to get over this shit.

31:25.500 --> 31:26.625
[STEP SQUEAKS]

31:31.542 --> 31:33.000
[HIGH-PITCHED TONE]

31:33.917 --> 31:35.125
[FAINT SCREAM]

31:37.917 --> 31:39.042
[HE WHIMPERS]

31:42.667 --> 31:44.250
[HE BREATHES HEAVILY]

31:45.625 --> 31:48.208
Baxter, come on.
- [DOG WHIMPERS]

31:49.542 --> 31:51.708
Bax, I'm not pissing around, pal.
Come on, shift it.

31:51.750 --> 31:54.000
[DOG WHIMPERS]

31:54.708 --> 31:55.667
Baxter!

31:55.958 --> 31:57.167
[DOG WHIMPERS]

32:00.375 --> 32:01.750
Jesus, dog, man.

32:03.000 --> 32:04.167
