32:11.917 --> 32:13.083
[HOUSE CREAKS]

32:17.625 --> 32:18.667
[HOUSE CREAKS]

32:19.500 --> 32:20.750
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

32:45.292 --> 32:47.042
[DOG WHIMPERS]
- [ERIC]: I know.

32:47.542 --> 32:49.792
We're not here to run away.
- [LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

32:55.500 --> 32:56.750
Why are we here, huh?

33:02.458 --> 33:03.500
Bax.

33:05.208 --> 33:06.292
Bax, come on.

33:07.208 --> 33:08.333
[HE WHISTLES TO DOG]

33:09.000 --> 33:09.875
Baxter.

33:17.875 --> 33:19.500
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

33:20.583 --> 33:23.000
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

33:34.708 --> 33:36.542
[THUNDER CRACKS]

33:41.000 --> 33:42.417
[DOOR CLATTERS]

33:45.250 --> 33:48.167
