[THUNDER ROARS]

34:12.333 --> 34:13.708
[THUNDER CLAPS]

34:35.625 --> 34:37.208
[THUNDER CLAPS]

34:40.792 --> 34:42.583
[BABY MURMURS]

34:43.000 --> 34:44.208
[DOOR OPENS]

34:44.917 --> 34:46.458
[METAL RATTLES]

34:55.708 --> 34:56.750
Bax.

34:56.792 --> 34:57.917
[DOG WHIMPERS]

34:58.417 --> 34:59.583
[THUNDER CLAPS]

35:00.292 --> 35:01.667
[WIND WHISTLES]

35:15.500 --> 35:16.583
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

35:19.083 --> 35:20.458
[FAINT CRIES]

35:32.250 --> 35:33.333
[STEP CREAKS]

35:35.417 --> 35:36.292
[THUNDER CLAPS]

35:42.250 --> 35:44.417
[STORM FADES]

36:03.792 --> 36:05.833
[RACHEL, VO]:
Let's drive up to the mountains.

36:05.917 --> 36:07.792
[ERIC, VO]: No.
- [RACHEL, VO]: Why?

36:07.875 --> 36:09.417
Still scared of heights?

36:09.458 --> 36:11.708
[SHE LAUGHS]

36:11.792 --> 36:13.292
[ERIC, VO]:
No, it's not that.

36:14.375 --> 36:15.792
[RACHEL, VO]:
Why, Eric?

36:16.083 --> 36:17.458
[ERIC, VO]:
I said no, Rach.

36:18.250 --> 36:20.167
[RACHEL ECHOES]:
Why?

36:21.000 --> 36:22.208
[ERIC, VO]:
Rachel.

36:23.542 --> 36:25.125
[WOMAN SCREAMS]

36:26.250 --> 36:27.583
[SCREAM FADES]

36:29.333 --> 36:31.000
[WIND HOWLS]

36:37.833 --> 36:39.833
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

36:47.292 --> 36:49.292
[HOUSE CREAKS]

36:52.875 --> 36:54.000
[HE WHISPERS]:
Baby steps.

36:54.833 --> 36:55.917
Baby steps.

36:57.417 --> 36:59.500
[HOUSE CREAKS]

37:15.000 --> 37:16.958
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

37:17.708 --> 37:19.667
[HOUSE CREAKS]

37:33.542 --> 37:36.333
[HE FLICKS LIGHTER OPEN AND SHUT]

37:43.542 --> 37:46.125
[HE CONTINUES FLICKING LIGHTER]

37:55.083 --> 37:57.167
[HE FLICKS LIGHTER]
- [LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

38:05.500 --> 38:07.500
[WIND HOWLS]

38:08.583 --> 38:11.250
[HE CONTINUES FLICKING LIGHTER]

38:15.042 --> 38:16.083
Come on.

38:21.333 --> 38:23.333
[SHEEP BLEAT]

38:48.542 --> 38:49.667
[HE EXHALES DEEPLY]

38:51.917 --> 38:53.417
[WHISPERING HOWL]

38:53.500 --> 38:56.000
[SHEEP BLEAT]
-[DOG BARKS]

38:57.458 --> 38:58.542
Who's there?

39:01.708 --> 39:03.292
Who's there?
- [DOG BARKS]

39:05.000 --> 39:06.000
Who's there?

39:10.125 --> 39:11.333
[WIND WHOOSHES]

39:11.417 --> 39:12.667
[SHEEP GO SILENT]

39:25.000 --> 39:26.250
Baxter.

39:26.542 --> 39:27.708
[HE SHOUTS]:
Baxter!

39:41.583 --> 39:42.875
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

40:05.708 --> 40:07.167
[NO DIAL TONE]

40:13.250 --> 40:14.667
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

