[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

41:09.417 --> 41:10.417
Hey!

41:21.417 --> 41:22.333
Hey!

41:26.583 --> 41:27.583
Hey!

41:33.083 --> 41:34.583
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

41:42.333 --> 41:44.875
[HIGH-PITCHED TONE]

42:08.292 --> 42:09.917
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

42:17.542 --> 42:18.667
[DOOR METAL CLANGS]

42:19.750 --> 42:20.875
[DOOR METAL CLANGS]

42:22.000 --> 42:23.042
[DOOR METAL CLANGS]

42:31.167 --> 42:32.917
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

42:47.958 --> 42:50.458
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

42:55.083 --> 42:56.167
[ERIC]:
It's tall.

43:04.917 --> 43:06.667
Now you can cheer up as well, mate.

43:07.750 --> 43:09.625
You've learnt
how to put the kettle on, aye?

43:10.125 --> 43:13.583
[HOUSE CREAKS]

43:14.708 --> 43:16.500
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

43:18.667 --> 43:19.625
Yeah.

43:20.958 --> 43:22.792
[HOUSE CREAKS DEEPLY]

43:27.083 --> 43:28.958
[HOUSE CREAKS LOUDLY]

43:32.375 --> 43:33.708
Get a grip, you sad bugger.

43:35.125 --> 43:36.458
[HE BREATHES DEEPLY]

43:37.500 --> 43:39.208
[HE PANTS]

43:51.958 --> 43:53.000
Baxter.

43:54.667 --> 43:56.000
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

43:56.083 --> 43:57.167
Baxter!

