48:21.667 --> 48:22.792
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

48:22.833 --> 48:24.583
Mum, wh... what are you doing here?

48:24.625 --> 48:28.250
Feed will get damp,
dumped aside in the shed like that.

48:29.375 --> 48:30.375
What?

48:32.208 --> 48:33.917
The place is falling apart.

48:34.667 --> 48:36.125
Roof needs seeing to.

48:36.500 --> 48:39.000
[SHE SIGHS]
Heaven help you, lad.

48:41.667 --> 48:43.417
How did you... how did you find me?

48:44.458 --> 48:47.292
I should've brought
your father's old tools.

48:47.667 --> 48:48.750
[CROCKERY SHATTERS]

48:50.167 --> 48:51.167
Oh!

48:51.708 --> 48:53.458
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

48:56.417 --> 48:57.708
[SHE GATHERS THE SHARDS]

48:57.792 --> 48:59.500
[SHEEP BLEATS]

48:59.583 --> 49:01.500
