to that... that...

49:20.958 --> 49:22.167
cheap harlot.

49:22.250 --> 49:24.500
That dirty, filthy whore!

49:24.583 --> 49:26.167
The fucking...

49:35.125 --> 49:36.167
[SHE GASPS]

49:41.083 --> 49:42.125
[SHE WHIMPERS]

49:49.125 --> 49:50.250
Why?

49:51.583 --> 49:52.958
Why, Eric?

49:54.708 --> 49:57.875
[SHE SOBS]
Why did you leave me there alone?

49:59.167 --> 50:02.417
Why did you let her take you away from me?

50:03.083 --> 50:07.083
[SHE WEEPS]

50:07.667 --> 50:08.667
[SHE CRIES]

50:09.208 --> 50:10.500
No!

50:10.583 --> 50:12.417
Get off me!
- Mum! Mum.

50:13.125 --> 50:14.167
Mum!

50:14.208 --> 50:15.833
[SHE WEEPS]

50:21.708 --> 50:23.292
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

50:25.375 --> 50:27.958
[SHE SOBS]

50:45.625 --> 50:47.125
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

50:47.167 --> 50:49.250
You've not been eating properly.

50:50.750 --> 50:53.208
Look at you.
You've got no colour in your cheeks.

50:55.292 --> 50:56.833
I've not had much of an appetite.

50:58.625 --> 51:00.250
Rachel, I suppose.

51:06.208 --> 51:07.792
How's Baxter doing?

51:08.458 --> 51:09.583
Yeah, he's erm...

51:13.000 --> 51:14.458
Still settling in, you know?

51:14.917 --> 51:19.375
I thought he'd love the change,
but he's been a bit... distant.

51:19.750 --> 51:21.583
[SHE TUTS]
Ah, is he six now?

51:22.583 --> 51:23.458
Eight.

51:24.333 --> 51:25.333
Eight?

51:29.708 --> 51:32.958
I remember how you were with Patch.

51:34.625 --> 51:37.250
He loved the outdoors. You both did.

51:39.167 --> 51:42.000
Everything was easier then, wasn't it?
- No.

51:43.167 --> 51:44.667
Just different.

51:45.667 --> 51:47.500
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

51:50.042 --> 51:52.250
God has a map for us all.

51:53.583 --> 51:56.875
You... you can stray from the path easily.

51:57.375 --> 52:00.875
But finding the path again,
that's the hardest thing.

52:00.958 --> 52:03.042
Look, if you've come to preach, then...

52:03.542 --> 52:04.667
Oh, no.

52:05.750 --> 52:06.750
No.

52:15.667 --> 52:16.875
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

52:16.917 --> 52:18.875
You still haven't answered my question.

52:24.917 --> 52:26.292
How did you find me here?

52:29.417 --> 52:31.542
All sheep end up at market.

52:34.208 --> 52:35.500
It's a small world.

52:36.542 --> 52:38.208
I hadn't even heard of this place.

52:39.875 --> 52:41.375
It's a far way out west.

52:43.333 --> 52:46.958
What made you think I'd farm again
somewhere else anyhow?

52:47.500 --> 52:49.958
You'll always pull back to what you know.

52:50.792 --> 52:52.958
You can't help but follow your blood.

52:55.125 --> 52:56.667
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

52:58.042 --> 52:59.917
I just wanted the space is all.

53:01.167 --> 53:03.667
Well, now she's out of the way.

53:04.417 --> 53:05.625
You're here.

53:06.958 --> 53:09.750
What?
- You used to be so happy.

53:10.208 --> 53:11.500
Before her.

53:11.875 --> 53:14.500
Before her drinking and her other men.

53:14.542 --> 53:16.750
Don't bring her into it.

53:17.292 --> 53:18.292
Alright?

53:25.000 --> 53:26.167
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

53:26.208 --> 53:27.292
Thank you.

53:32.375 --> 53:33.875
Just accept it.

53:35.000 --> 53:36.542
It'll make it easier for yourself.

53:36.583 --> 53:38.375
Why don't you ever listen, Mum?

53:38.417 --> 53:41.000
I know it was all too much for you.

53:44.875 --> 53:46.208
It's nothing to do with you.

53:48.500 --> 53:51.417
She was a selfish, ungodly whore.

53:54.125 --> 53:56.083
I hope it hurt her, Eric.

53:56.375 --> 53:57.250
The crash.

54:05.667 --> 54:06.750
I hope it wasn't quick.

54:08.125 --> 54:12.750
I hope she felt a slow, burning agony
in the final moments.

54:14.792 --> 54:16.583
The agony she caused others.

54:18.125 --> 54:21.667
I hope the hot flames of the wreck
were the last thing she felt

54:21.750 --> 54:24.583
before she was cast down
into the fires of hell.

54:24.958 --> 54:27.000
Get out... Get out of my house.

54:27.083 --> 54:29.083
One thing you can be sure of.

54:29.667 --> 54:30.792
That baby.

54:31.708 --> 54:32.958
It wasn't yours.

54:35.375 --> 54:37.125
Likely the devil's child.

54:38.792 --> 54:40.875
Oh, it's a bastard.

54:43.792 --> 54:46.542
You did the right thing, son.
- Mum...

54:46.625 --> 54:47.917
You did the right thing.

54:49.750 --> 54:51.417
You did the right thing.

54:51.875 --> 54:54.250
Mum!
- [SHE SCREAMS DEMONICALLY]

