57:02.000 --> 57:03.167
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Yes, why?

57:05.167 --> 57:06.292
Just wondering.

57:08.167 --> 57:09.250
[FISHERWOMAN]:
So.

57:10.375 --> 57:12.042
