57:13.917 --> 57:14.917
Sorry?

57:15.792 --> 57:18.417
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Questioning yourself already, Mr Black.

57:19.583 --> 57:21.625
Um... my... my dog...

57:22.125 --> 57:23.250
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Your dog?

57:25.125 --> 57:26.708
Baxter. He's not here.

57:26.750 --> 57:28.042
[FISHERWOMAN]:
He's run away.

57:30.292 --> 57:31.792
