1:13:30.958 --> 1:13:32.750
[PHONE CONTINUES RINGING]

1:13:41.208 --> 1:13:43.167
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

1:13:43.250 --> 1:13:45.583
[LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

1:13:49.917 --> 1:13:50.917
Where am I?

1:13:53.542 --> 1:13:55.875
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Only you can answer that, Mr Black.

1:13:56.750 --> 1:13:59.167
Only you know why you are where you are.

1:14:01.542 --> 1:14:02.667
I don't understand.

1:14:03.625 --> 1:14:05.000
[FISHERWOMAN]:
But you do, son.

1:14:06.333 --> 1:14:08.542
Surely you've come to realise by now.

1:14:12.333 --> 1:14:15.250
Am... am I dead?
- [LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

1:14:17.292 --> 1:14:19.292
[FISHERWOMAN]:
I don't know what you are.

1:14:24.125 --> 1:14:25.125
Are you?

1:14:31.042 --> 1:14:33.083
I want... I want to go home.

1:14:36.125 --> 1:14:37.958
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Where is home, Mr Black?

1:14:40.000 --> 1:14:41.417
You can't keep me here.

1:14:43.167 --> 1:14:44.875
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Is that what I'm doing?

1:14:45.500 --> 1:14:46.958
I don't know what you're doing.

1:14:48.292 --> 1:14:49.708
I... I want to go home.

1:14:50.708 --> 1:14:54.792
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Maybe, Mr Black, maybe you are home.

1:14:55.292 --> 1:14:57.167
This... this isn't my home.

1:14:58.250 --> 1:15:01.625
[FISHERWOMAN]:
And what is it, son, if not your home?

1:15:02.833 --> 1:15:04.625
It's... it's a fucking prison!

1:15:06.167 --> 1:15:07.875
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Is that what you think it is?

1:15:10.375 --> 1:15:11.458
[HE SNIFFLES]

1:15:12.583 --> 1:15:15.042
You can't... you can't leave me here.
- [LIGHTHOUSE BELL TOLLS]

1:15:15.083 --> 1:15:17.792
[FISHERWOMAN]:
But maybe you need to be there.

1:15:19.333 --> 1:15:21.250
I don't need to be anywhere.

1:15:22.417 --> 1:15:24.208
[FISHERWOMAN]:
We all need our place, son.

1:15:25.583 --> 1:15:27.417
Perhaps that's yours now.

1:15:29.583 --> 1:15:31.375
But I didn't do anything.

1:15:31.708 --> 1:15:33.167
[FISHERWOMAN]:
What does that mean?

1:15:33.792 --> 1:15:35.500
It means I didn't do anything.

1:15:36.042 --> 1:15:37.542
[FISHERWOMAN]:
What didn't you do, Mr Black?

1:15:37.625 --> 1:15:38.625
Nothing!

1:15:38.792 --> 1:15:40.375
[FISHERWOMAN]:
No one does nothing.

1:15:40.417 --> 1:15:41.667
It was an accident.

1:15:48.750 --> 1:15:50.292
It was an accident.

1:15:54.083 --> 1:15:55.083
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Your wife.

1:15:58.708 --> 1:15:59.833
[ERIC]:
It was an accident.

1:16:04.333 --> 1:16:05.542
[FISHERWOMAN]:
You were there.

1:16:07.583 --> 1:16:09.250
[ERIC BREATHES HEAVILY]

1:16:09.458 --> 1:16:10.708
[ERIC]:
I'd been drinking.

1:16:11.875 --> 1:16:13.042
I'd been drinking.

1:16:18.083 --> 1:16:19.292
I lost control.

1:16:21.042 --> 1:16:21.958
[WOMAN SCREAMS]

1:16:33.500 --> 1:16:34.500
[ERIC]:
Ran away.

1:16:36.667 --> 1:16:37.625
I ran away.

1:16:39.792 --> 1:16:42.125
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Where, Mr Black?

1:16:43.708 --> 1:16:44.917
I don't... I don't know.

1:16:46.875 --> 1:16:49.708
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Do you think your wife is still alive?

1:16:50.292 --> 1:16:52.042
Don't know. I don't know.

1:16:54.875 --> 1:16:57.208
[FISHERWOMAN]:
There was another, wasn't there?

1:16:59.000 --> 1:17:00.000
A baby.

1:17:01.125 --> 1:17:02.292
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Yes.

1:17:05.958 --> 1:17:08.583
What a curse to live with, Mr Black.

1:17:13.833 --> 1:17:14.833
Yes.

1:17:17.000 --> 1:17:19.250
[FISHERWOMAN]:
Time to begin your sentence, son.

